attributionInfo.brokerName: Better Homes and Gardens Real Estate Foothills

data.description: Step into tranquility! This charming home features 3 cozy bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms with the master suite having two closets!  Just inside the front door, you'll find a warm livingroom area with gas fireplace and vaulted ceiling. Adjacent the livingroom is a dining area and beautful kitchen with stainless appliances. A bonus feature of this home is the bright sunroom.  Outside, the inviting pool creates a peaceful oasis with plenty of room for entertaining under the pergola and around the pool. During the summer, the trees bloom perfectly to create privacy!  Ideally situated with easy access to I-40, this home offers both comfort and convenience. Arrange a viewing today and experience the cozy charm for yourself!  This is one home you will NOT want to miss!
